@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Overall System Flow

participant Docker
participant Zookeeper
participant Kafka
participant Producer
participant Consumer

Docker -> Zookeeper: Start Container
Docker -> Kafka: Start Container
Kafka -> Zookeeper: Connect & Register

Producer -> Kafka: Connect to Broker
Consumer -> Kafka: Connect to Broker

Producer -> Kafka: Send Message 1
Producer -> Kafka: Send Message 2
Producer -> Kafka: Send Message 3

Kafka -> Consumer: Deliver Message 1
Kafka -> Consumer: Deliver Message 2
Kafka -> Consumer: Deliver Message 3

Consumer -> Consumer: Process & Display

@enduml

